data.description: *OPEN HOUSE SAT AND SUN 12/2 & 12/3 FROM 11AM-1PM* WOW! SELLER OFFERING $5,000 FOR BUYER'S RATE BUY-DOWN ON THE LOWEST PRICED 4 BEDROOM HOME IN STILLWATER RANCH!! Come see this Energy Efficient, 1 owner home loaded w/ updates and upgrades to include spray foam insulation w/ semi-conditioned attic space, cellulose wall insulation, double pane low E3 vinyl windows, Trane HVAC system *Seller used front 4th bedroom as TV/Media room* Very well maintained 1 story home, 4 SIDED BRICK, with 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths don't come around often. Close to major highways, outstanding schools, Lackland AFB, parks and great restaurants!  Please drive by the wonderful community center with 2 pools, park, sports courts, clubhouse and more! Other upgrades include full sprinkler system, Texas Blue water softening system, 2 recently installed (2021) water heaters, garage "pet sink", prewired for surround sound in FR and back deck, tile in wet areas/light oak wood floors in dining room/ carpet in bedrooms, Beam Central Vacuum system thru-out home, Stainless built-in appliances, Granite tops, Custom cabinetry and much more!!!  Schedule a showing with your Realtor TODAY!!
